ting that $\\beta$ is getting set by a global process\ndriven by the scale of the galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 May 2020 18:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Jan 2021 19:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-24"}
