ulated proton-proton collisions within the CMS\ndetector. We study the scaling of the algorithm as a function of the parallel\nresources utilized and find large speedups both from vectorization and\nmulti-threading. mkFit achieves a speedup of a factor of 6 compared to the\nnominal algorithm when run in a single-threaded application within the CMS\nsoftware framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 May 2020 20:35:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jul 2020 19:03:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-30"}
