ement with theoretical calculations. The single\ndifferential cross sections are also in overall good agreement with theoretical\npredictions, except at very forward muon scattering angles that correspond to\nlow momentum-transfer events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 May 2020 22:48:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2020 17:37:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 6 Oct 2020 02:46:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-18"}
