nge. Our team\n(ustc-nelslip) ranked 1st in track II, and 3rd in track I. The code is\navailable at https://github.com/gniknoil/FG2020-kinship.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 May 2020 01:43:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 7 Jun 2020 12:19:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-09"}
